Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来 捂住耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来换我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.79,0:21:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
